      "title": "Drug pills worth Rs 29.7 million recovered",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "2,973 narcotic pills sent to the Central Post Office have been seized by the Customs.",
        "The total value of the said drug baths is reported to be around 29.7 million rupees.",
        "Also, the spokesperson of the Customs Department has said that these drug baths have been sent from the Netherlands. (a)"
